---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Kiku Studio — Offline-First Podcast Studio for Android" description="Record, anonymize voices, transcribe offline, and share — all on your Android phone. Built for journalists who can't trust the cloud.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-icon">
      <img src="/icon-studio.svg" alt="Kiku Studio" class="hero-icon-svg" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-badge">Offline-First Studio</div>
    <h1>Record. Protect.<br/>Share safely.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      The podcast studio that works without internet, without sending your data anywhere,
      and helps obscure your source's identity.
    </p>
    <!-- <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wharfe.kikustudio" class="cta">Get on Google Play</a> -->
    <p class="coming-soon">Coming soon to Google Play</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Scenario: Daniel -->
  <section class="scenario">
    <div class="scenario-quote">
      <p>"I interview whistleblowers. Their voices are pitch-shifted before the recording leaves my device. Everything runs offline — no data sent to any server."</p>
      <cite>— Daniel, 35, Central America. Investigative journalist.</cite>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="feature highlight">
      <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F6E1;</div>
      <h3>Voice Anonymization</h3>
      <p>Pitch-shift voice modification to help reduce speaker recognizability. Adjustable strength. Designed for source protection.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature highlight">
      <div class="feature-icon">&#x2708;</div>
      <h3>Fully Offline</h3>
      <p>AI noise reduction, voice anonymization, transcription — all on-device after one-time model download. No internet required. No data leaves your phone.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature highlight">
      <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F6AB;</div>
      <h3>No Metadata</h3>
      <p>Exported audio files contain no location, device info, or timestamps in the file data. UUID filenames prevent timing analysis.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F399;</div>
      <h3>Field Recording</h3>
      <p>48kHz lossless recording with real-time monitoring, pause/resume, Bluetooth warning, and storage checks.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F916;</div>
      <h3>AI Noise Reduction</h3>
      <p>DeepFilterNet3 removes background noise on-device. One tap to studio quality — no cloud, no cost.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F4CA;</div>
      <h3>Waveform Editor</h3>
      <p>Cut, trim, undo/redo with pinch-to-zoom. Chapter markers for show notes. Export clips for social media.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F4DD;</div>
      <h3>On-Device Transcription</h3>
      <p>whisper.cpp running locally on your phone. Or bring your own OpenAI API key. Copy or share transcription text directly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F465;</div>
      <h3>Double-Ender Recording</h3>
      <p>Each participant records locally. Auto-align by timestamp, mix with smart silence compression — no call quality compromise.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F4E4;</div>
      <h3>Clip & Share</h3>
      <p>Select a highlight, export as a clip, and share directly via WhatsApp, Telegram, or any app. Perfect for social media.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Scenario: Priya -->
  <section class="scenario">
    <div class="scenario-quote">
      <p>"I record interviews at the local market, remove the noise with one tap, cut the best parts, and share the episode — all from my phone. No PC needed."</p>
      <cite>— Priya, 32, Mumbai. Independent podcaster, publishes biweekly.</cite>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="privacy-note">
    <h2>A note on privacy</h2>
    <p>
      Kiku Studio is free, with no ads and no tracking. Voice anonymization uses pitch shifting,
      which helps reduce speaker recognizability but cannot guarantee complete anonymity — speech patterns,
      content, and environmental sounds may still allow identification by a determined adversary.
      For maximum protection, combine with device encryption and a strong lock screen.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="specs">
    <h2>Technical Details</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>48kHz / 16-bit mono PCM recording</li>
      <li>DeepFilterNet3 noise reduction (Rust/JNI, on-device)</li>
      <li>TD-PSOLA voice anonymization (pure Kotlin, no dependencies)</li>
      <li>whisper.cpp on-device transcription (C/JNI, ~75MB model download)</li>
      <li>EBU R128 loudness normalization (-16 LUFS)</li>
      <li>Energy-based Voice Activity Detection for silence trimming</li>
      <li>Non-destructive waveform editing with 20-level undo</li>
      <li>Chapter markers with timestamp export</li>
      <li>UUID filenames, no metadata in exports, FLAG_SECURE option</li>
      <li>Requires Android 8.0+, recommended Android 10+ with 4GB+ RAM</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Listen with Kiku Player</h2>
    <p>Smart Speed, AI summaries, and real-time transcripts for any audio.</p>
    <a href="/player" class="cta-link">Learn about Kiku Player &rarr;</a>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 6rem 0 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: var(--color-primary-light);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero-icon-svg {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-primary-container);
    color: var(--color-on-primary-container);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .coming-soon {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .scenario {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }
  .scenario-quote {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary-light);
    background: var(--color-surface-variant);
    border-radius: 0 0.75rem 0.75rem 0;
  }
  .scenario-quote p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-on-surface);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .scenario-quote cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  }
  .feature {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--color-surface-variant);
  }
  .feature.highlight {
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary-light);
  }
  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .feature p {
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .privacy-note {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-surface-variant);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .privacy-note h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .privacy-note p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .specs {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }
  .specs h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .specs ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant);
  }
  .specs li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--color-on-surface-variant);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .cta-link {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
</style>
